Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.nlp.Place
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Place
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Information about a place required by NLP. Information may be obtained from search or other sources and transformed into this by application.

    IMPORTANT: Natural language processor is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.
